org.dsngroup.broke.client.storage

Class FakePublishMessageQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dsngroup.broke.client.storage.FakePublishMessageQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPublishMessageQueue

    public class FakePublishMessageQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPublishMessageQueue
    A message queue for storing PUBLISH messages from the server The isBackPressured status is emulated as follow: 1. After the PUBLISH received is more than maxSize, set isBackPressured to true 2. Start a thread that will set the isBackPressured to false after a fixed time.
